    <Data><![CDATA[<h1>Definition</h1>
  <p>Avoid exposing information that is not required. By doing so, you are potentially opening doors that can lead to additional vulnerabilities. Also, handle errors gracefully; don't expose any more information than is required when returning an error message to the end user. </p>]]></Data>
